item.title: CVE-2023-0658|2024-08-02T05:17:50.360Z -- multilaser -- re057
item.description: A vulnerability, which was classified as critical, was found in Multilaser RE057 and RE170 2.1/2.2. This affects an unknown part of the file /param.file.tgz of the component Backup File Handler. The manipulation leads to information disclosure. It is possible to initiate the attack remotely. The identifier VDB-220053 was assigned to this vulnerability. Es wurde eine kritische Schwachstelle in Multilaser RE057 and RE170 2.1/2.2 gefunden. Dabei betrifft es einen unbekannter Codeteil der Datei /param.file.tgz der Komponente Backup File Handler.
